I am looking for assistance to recruit 4 people to my team - I need help to find 4 new team members by Monday the 22nd (GMT). 

A brief over view of the opportunity is as follows;

To ensure the success of our team and that each candidate is committed

Looking for a qualified Economist or Business Analyst who can undertake Market Research and provide short reports from time to time;
1. World Economy situation over from beginning of 2019 and outlook for the rest of the year,
2. Economic Recession prosp

Hi;
I am the owner of an orthodontic and dental clinic in Lebanon.
My vision for my clinic and website is to be a platform for researched educational content in the form of text and videos and drive marketing through online content, SEO and presentation

Looking for virtual assistant to regularly assist Managing Director with the following tasks:
email management (review/triage/drafting responses); 
calendar management; 
administrative assistance: including help with correspondence, production of repor
